<template>
  <form @submit.prevent="uploadFile">
    <input type="file" ref="fileInput" />
    <button type="submit">Upload</button>
  </form>
</template>

<script>
import api from "../api/api";
export default {
  methods: {
    uploadFile() {
      const formData = new FormData();
      formData.append("file", this.$refs.fileInput.files[0]);
      "upload",
        {
          method: "POST",
          body: formData,
        };
    },
  },
};
</script>
